data.description: Welcome to this beautiful corner lot in Sweetgrass community! This home sits in a quiet neighborhood and offers quick access to the highway and only 10 minutes away from the Denver Premium Outlets. The impeccable maintained home is move in ready. The main level features a spacious living room and family room that includes a cozy fireplace. The kitchen features granite counter tops that is highlighted with newer stainless steel appliances and a spacious area to host parties. The roomy basement includes a large finished bedroom with a fully updated bathroom. Walking upstairs includes a luminous master bedroom with a very roomy walk-in closet, 2 additional bedrooms that is next to a full bathroom. Stepping outside offers a cared for lawn with a wood deck and a lot of room to host parties. In addition, new water heater installed 2022, all appliances included, (Washer and Dryer are new as of 2022, fridge purchased 2021).
